Zadanie 2¶

Uruchomi i zmierzy czasy dziaania obydwu funkcji - kadej dla rnych rozmiarw wektorw. Dokona 10 pomiarw dla kadego rozmiaru wektora

In [16]:
#creating stucture to store execution time results

using DataFrames 
data = [50,100,300,500,750,1000]
storage = DataFrame()
n = length(data)*10

storage.scalar_productTime = zeros(n)
storage.multiply_matrixTime = zeros(n)
storage.vector_size = zeros(n)

show(storage)

In [17]:
counter = 1
for i in 1:(length(data))
    v1 = rand(-100:100, data[i])
    v2 = rand(-100:100, data[i])
    v3 = rand(-100:100, data[i])
    matrix = rand(-100:100, data[i], data[i])
    for j in 1:10
        storage[counter , 1] = @elapsed scalar_product(v1,v2)
        storage[counter , 2] = @elapsed multiply_matrix(matrix,v3)
        storage[counter,3] = data[i]
        counter+=1
        
    end
end

show(storage)

using Statistics

mean_stats = DataFrame()
grouped = DataFrame()
grouped = groupby(new_df, :vector_size)
mean_stats = combine(grouped, "scalar_productTime" => mean, "multiply_matrixTime" => mean)
